  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8465950/" class="title-link">《胡塞尔现象学概念通释》新版测评暨纪念胡塞尔...</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8465950"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/stone1919/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u2283048-2.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/stone1919/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">刘石桐</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2017-04-08"
      class="main-meta">2017-04-08 15:07:46</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8465950_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  倪先生的《通释》是我最爱不释手的一本现象学工具书（不要逼我承认是因为看不懂Husserl Lexikon），1999、2007、2016三个版本已集齐（能不能召唤点啥？） 基本数据：二版，597页，49元；三版，638页，68元，稍微厚一点点，近十年过去涨价也不多，相当良心。 不过与第二版修订达...

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                        <span class="publisher left">
                            商务印书馆2016版</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8465950_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8465950_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
